{"tid":636331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好悶有無人想一齊無聊玩下brainstorm? [sosad]","createTime":"2018-04-20T17:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T13:37:34.000Z","uid":15823,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a47985e865cf60510795546897de51e9368281f3","tid":636331,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:47:03.000Z","msg":"順便俾個機會自己榨下個腦諗緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n少少建議玩法，其實好free 你想點玩都得，唔一定要跟:<br />\n<ins>玩:</ins><br />\n1. 自己諗個詞語做中心波波開始，用mindmap 形式去擴大，例如: *(貓)-&gt;(橙色)-&gt;(橙)-&gt;...<br />\n2. 搵張白紙寫滿佢為完成，盡量少空白啦，榨到個腦盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 唔好花太多時間諗即刻寫，九唔搭八都無所謂，可用句子，詞語，手繪或任何形式，任何語言<br />\n4. 寫滿後揀三個波你最想分享既，用幾句講下佢地對你黎講有咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 如果無特別想講既波波，可以分享下今次思路有關既感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或最長果條路有無特別意思可以令你諗到咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6. 貼返你寫完張圖係基本啦，不過唔好就咁掉張圖出黎乜感想都無，呢度唔係showoff 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且其實係無野好showoff <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7. 唔好刪唔好改<br />\n8. 唔好重覆<br />\n<br />\n<ins>出題:</ins><br />\n1. 可以隨便掉個詞語出題俾人玩<br />\n2. 用人題目既就要由呢個詞語為中心開始<br />\n3. 用人題目一定要quote 返出題果條友個post，容易跟返<br />\n<br />\n<ins>開始之前一d 建議：</ins><br />\n1. 先身處一個舒適既環境，開始之前咩都唔好做住，冥想一陣或聽首音樂集中精神先開始<br />\n2. 唔好玩太密，好易俾上一次個思路影響你去諗差唔多既野<br />\n4. 紙筆寫比電腦畫好<br />\n5. 一次過完成晒先做其他野，唔好分心住<br />\n6. 張圖唔好打側出，咁多字要睇好辛苦，中bug 另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7. 貼之前check 下你張圖先唔好自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52af4b130641efbd8f7b1ddd497e79574ccca528","tid":636331,"uid":15823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/013108_15a69b08d680bebd5e3a644b37555f10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F013108_15a69b08d680bebd5e3a644b37555f10.png&h=023032ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. (紅軸): 買左個keyboard 期待緊佢送黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. (前兩日黎interview 條友): 黎in programmer 但cv 寫佢打字好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後in 完唔啱駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. (搵d 有用既sfx for game): 整緊隻驚，會搵辦法自己錄又好，買又好搵d sound effect 返黎。同埋仲要搵d graphic source 返黎做layout，好想今年內推到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b269b8f9439e6fcae3a9557f51d5c4a2f23704","tid":636331,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"順手放低題目:<br />\n<br />\n(火險)"},{"pid":"55c9fbf9f3688edc96d7b50b663a761067df4c6a","tid":636331,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T20:11:29.000Z","msg":"好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448752a3fc1050dd4d15979c82d52d77d9549fd5","tid":636331,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b269b8f9439e6fcae3a9557f51d5c4a2f23704","tid":636331,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"順手放低題目:<br />\n<br />\n(火險)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"個題目liu lung到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a218c2877fc1ec1bbc5e9cf384afdf1057f2e0","tid":636331,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"448752a3fc1050dd4d15979c82d52d77d9549fd5","tid":636331,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b269b8f9439e6fcae3a9557f51d5c4a2f23704","tid":636331,"uid":15823,"like":0,"d